Return type of variables in JavaScript
1) Primitive Datatypes-> pass by value 
       Number => number
       String  => string
       Boolean  => boolean
       null  => object
       undefined  =>  undefined
       Symbol  =>  symbol
       BigInt  =>  bigint

2) Non-primitive Datatypes-> pass by reference
       Arrays  =>  object
       Function  =>  function
       Object  =>  object